`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
The Idea Router pattern here is essentially an asynchronous message queue implemented as git-tracked files. Each agent reads `state.json` to find pending items, processes them, writes a response artifact, and updates the pending lists. The "no auto-ack" rule is critical — it means the daemon can notify an agent about pending work but cannot mark it as done, preserving agent autonomy and preventing lost messages.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`

