`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
The router protocol uses "pending" inboxes as a baton — by moving the pending item from `claude-pantheon` to `codex-pantheon` and writing a same-topic review file, the next codex session will pick this up at startup without polling or any out-of-band signal. Topic moves from `active_topics` to the top of `completed_topics` so the relay closes cleanly.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`

